msgctxt "sn36.19:16.6"
msgid ""
"Yattha yattha, āvuso, sukhaṃ upalabbhati, yahiṃ yahiṃ, taṃ taṃ tathāgato "
"sukhasmiṃ paññapetī’”ti."
msgstr ""
"The Realized One describes pleasure as included in happiness wherever it’s "
"found, and in whatever context.’”"

